descriptionHtml:
Now Breezehome lives up to it\'s name !!! 
Add\'s two see-through windows with curtins and shutters downstaires of Breezehome, just a little bit of eye-candy right now but I am going to be makeing it beter so let me know if you like and indorse. \"I get a very open relaxing feeling when I sit and drink an ale while I injoy the breeze buy the fire.\" Just for look\'s right now so no animation outside except for fire and smoke, night and day, I just needed to take a break and play the game for a while, but I will be adding to it very soon. I think this mod has potencial and I would like to hear some feedback, hope you injoy it as much as I do. Those of you who changed Whiterun it might look different depending on the mod, it was created with the vanilla Whiterun in mind for now, sorry.
